 features for PC gaming, but as an Android device, it cannot compete with the ease of use or comfort of smartphones and tablets. Still, the Nvidia Shield is the only handheld console that lets you remotely access your home computer and stream your PC games from anywhere in the world."]},"id":"71dea212-07e6-4cf0-84b9-6f7699bafbcc","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_59817","url":"/nvidia-shield-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-staff","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-staff","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Staff","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"EcXXb3s8QKwvex3rQshgX5","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-06-23T19:50:54Z","datePublished":"2014-06-23T19:50:54Z","name":"Nvidia Shield","synopsis":"The Nvidia Shield aims to offer an experience that no other handheld game console can: mobile streaming of your PC games. It features a 5-inch HD touchscreen, incredibly powerful components and a six-hour battery life.","review":{"rating":86,"verdict":"While most handheld game consoles offer unique mobile experiences, the Nvidia Shield lets you play your PC games on a mobile device.","pros":["The Nvidia Shield allows you to remotely wake up your home computer and play games from anywhere in the world."],"cons":["The handheld&#039;s touchscreen is clunky when playing Android games, and you have to own a GeForce graphics card to stream from your PC."]},"strapline":"The Nvidia Shield aims to offer an experience that no other handheld game console can: mobile streaming of your PC games. It features a 5-inch HD touchscreen, incredibly powerful components and a six-hour battery life.","language":"en","dateModified":"2014-06-23T19:50:54Z","id":"viYSLC6yhcZgcYevKNJUzQ","meta":{"title":"Nvidia Shield Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"The Nvidia Shield is the only handheld PC console, allowing you to download Android games 